dan membaca bintang.


48
00:06:41.790 --> 00:06:45.940
Dia mengatur jalur pulang kerumah,
dan kelelahan, tertidur.


49
00:06:47.840 --> 00:06:49.680
Awan menggulung.

50
00:06:51.060 --> 00:06:56.900
